-- UN's Envoys May Consider a Two-Year Kyoto Extension, Climate Group Says
-- B y   M a t h e w   C a r r
-- 2010-12-08T12:41:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-08/un-s-envoys-may-consider-a-two-year-kyoto-extension-climate-group-says.html
United Nations envoys may this week
consider a two-year extension for the Kyoto protocol beyond 2012
at climate-protection talks in Cancun, Mexico, Climate Group
said in an e-mailed statement today.  “Those close to the Japanese government consider it an
unlikely solution, while others have questioned the legal
feasibility of creating such an extension,” the lobby said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mathew Carr in London at 
